_sText:
CSGO Port by granis: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2194470311

Two staged tier 5 map which can be played like a linear, surf made by 15 people, led&detailed by masog.

MAP SPECIFIC SETTINGS

• sv_maxvelocity 5000

• tier 5 map intended for 64/66 tickrate

• s1 start boost is intended to boost exactly to 1775 u/s (while holding W)

• s2 start boost is intended to boost exactly to 1000 u/s (while holding W)

MAP ZONING

• !r should teleport player to map_desti

• stage teleports should teleport to s1_desti_wall and s2_desti

• s1 startzone trigger is called s1_startzone

• s2 startzone trigger is called s2_startzone

• map endzone trigger is called map_endzone

BONUS ZONING

• b1 startzone trigger is called bonus1_startzone

• b1 endzone trigger is called bonus1_endzone

• b2 startzone trigger is called bonus2_startzone

• b2 endzone trigger is called bonus2_endzone
